# Victualler Row — Illustration Prompt

Create a richly detailed, roughly square digital painting sized to sit beside narrative text on desktop or mobile screens. Depict a grounded late-medieval harbor campaign setting with food stalls, hanging onions, fish brine tubs, cabbage heaps, pork, baskets, and muddy paving. Emphasize crisp readability, brighter maritime color accents, and clear spatial separation more than muddy painterly atmosphere.

- Composition: narrow market row of provisioning stalls with the storehouse return path still easy to read.
- Key elements: cabbages, salted meat, eels, ale casks, ropes of onions, and rank class-marked food supplies.
- Character focus: victuallers whose setup makes clear that better food goes to important people.
- Navigation hint: keep the path back toward the salt storehouse visually direct and unmistakable.

